dc_description_s: This data represents addresses for Sheboygan County, Wisconsin in 2019. [Site address points represent the location of site or service delivery addresses assigned by local governments. Sheboygan County Planning & Conservation Department assigns and enters all addresses outside of Cities & Villages. All City & Village addresses are entered when the Planning Department is informed of them.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most recent data for this county, please visit:  https://geospatialhub-shebco.hub.arcgis.com/pages/open-data
